Usage: setSelectedPtnPinBlk [-help] <x1> <y1> <x2> <y2> <PtnPinBlkName>
                            <layerID>

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
<x1>                              # X1 (float, required)
<y1>                              # Y1 (float, required)
<x2>                              # X2 (float, required)
<y2>                              # Y2 (float, required)
<PtnPinBlkName>                   # name of the partition pin blockage
                                  # (string, required)
<layerID>                         # metal layer(s) that can route through the
                                  # partition feedthrough (string, required)